        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the potatoes are cooking, peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
