    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
