    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> cooked potatoes </strong>and <strong>blanched peas</strong> to the pan with your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, a<strong> </strong>pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and<strong> </strong>100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[175ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 4-5 min or until thickened</p>",
