    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the curry is cooking, add your<strong> naan[s] </strong>to a <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once thickened, remove the curry from the heat and stir through <strong>half</strong> your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(you’ll use the rest later!) – this is your<strong> pea & potato curry</strong></p>",
