      "instruction": "<p>To build, spread your<strong> mango chutney</strong> onto the<strong> warmed naan</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> pea & potato curry</strong> then dollop over the <strong>remaining natural yoghurt </strong>– this is your<strong> pea & potato curry loaded naan</strong></p><p>Season generously with <strong>black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
